ABOUT SQMUSIC<br><br>

SQMUSIC is a music project that explores different sounds, styles, and emotions through sound.<br><br>

Started in 2023, the project focuses on experimenting with genres — from energetic and experimental tracks to more melodic and atmospheric vibes.<br><br>

Each release is created with a simple idea: sound should feel alive and different every time.<br><br>

SQMUSIC was originally founded in France, but at the moment it is not fixed to a specific location and is still deciding where it will be based in the future.<br><br>

The project continues to grow across platforms like SoundCloud, TikTok, Instagram, and others, building its own creative identity.<br><br>

────────────────────<br><br>

SQMUSIC RECORDS<br><br>

SQMUSIC RECORDS is a label founded in mid-2024.<br><br>

It is currently under development and being shaped into a platform that will support future releases and creative projects.<br><br>

